73
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,439
Let's go.

74
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,480
Both of you, have a seat.

75
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,360
Okay, look at the camera.

76
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:38,680
Smile.

77
00:04:40,279 --> 00:04:42,079
Three, two...

78
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:42,780
