into the ocean with the setting sun♪

211
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:34,380
♪Butterfly leaves the land of taboo♪

212
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:39,660
♪The rotten mud rots away the malice♪

213
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:48,420
♪The fallen
naively wipes away the color♪

214
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:55,620
♪The soul wakes up
in the dangerous forest♪

215
00:13:57,020 --> 00:14:02,820
♪Crushing the mundane
and everchanging mask step by step♪

216
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:08,300
♪The crow stops whispering in the fog♪

217
00:14:09,260 --> 00:14:17,100
♪Black rose blooms
at the end of the abyss♪

218
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:22,900
♪It is a beautiful scar on my wound♪

219
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:26,380
♪Overcoming hardships♪

220
00:14:26,380 --> 00:14:32,700
♪A strong armor
wards off criticisms and disputes♪

221
00:14:33,340 --> 00:14:37,260
♪My brilliant life♪

222
00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:41,780
♪No matter who says anything♪

223
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:45,460
♪I won't be hurt anymore♪

224
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:51,780
♪If kindness goes away,
I'd rather be sharp♪
